title: Yann LeCun confirms his new ‘world model’ startup, reportedly seeks $5B+ valuation
description: Renowned AI scientist Yann LeCun confirmed on Thursday the worst-kept secret in the tech world: that he had indeed launched a new startup. Although he did say he will not be running the new company as its CEO.
